# The entire `ir/` tree is committed lifter output — IR dumps and the
# generated Rust source under `ir/raw-rs/` (all carry `@generated` or are
# pinned byte-for-byte by regen-or-fail tests). Marking them generated
# tells GitHub Linguist to collapse them in pull-request diffs and exclude
# them from language stats, so reviews focus on the hand-written sources.
ir/** linguist-generated=true
